# Phase A i64 fixture: declare an extern with Int64 params + result, then call it
# with i64 arguments produced via the @toInt64 cast.  Exercises:
#   - parseTypeName recognising Int64
#   - compiler-api resolveTypeName mapping Int64 → 'i64'
